  "help": [
    {
      "textLabel": "Human Life Value (HLV) is the present value of all future income you would expect to earn for your loved ones. It is an indicator of the the economic loss your family would suffer in the unfortunate event of your early death. This tool helps you calculate HLV, an important factor in determining the life insurance coverage amount you need to financially protect your family's future. For further information, please consult an insurance professional."
    }
  ],
